				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Important song for Vindi raid<a name="11273"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 6 03 7:20 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi all, just to let ya know, my guild has been taking out Vindi for a while now, with as little as 18 people, we are not elemental or even close though we do have an average raid level of 63 when raidiing.  After about the third Vindi kill, I wanted to try something a bit different.  I am usually the one who gets the honor of pulling Vindi with guards to the camp.  When I get Vindi to  camp, I fade to erase agro, then Highsun the guards to their spawn points.  Highsun rocks for this kill, when they get back i send em back again.  I have even high sunned Vindi back when he took down the main tank so the clerics could camp before we would wipe.  Highsun is definitely a song I keep loaded with this raid, it is VERY usefull.  I love seeing the off tank spinning around looking for his mob when it gates, or the first time when we were about to wipe and the raid force sees Vindi gate....very funny.  Of course I had to be very accute when telling people time and time again to camp NOW.  I do have JM1 and am level 65, highsun is rarely resisted.  Just wanted to share that info with you all, it has helped our growing guild a lot.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
